(70, 37, 'MOH. SYAEFUL EFFENDI<br>Student of Informatic Engineering Sebelas Maret University<br>Cirebon, Jawa Barat, Indonesia<br>ABOUT ME<br>I am a student in the Diploma Program (D3) of Informatics<br>KONTAK<br>Engineering at Sebelas Maret University. I have a strong interest<br>in back-end <span style=\"background-color: yellow\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow\">develop</span>ment</span>, but I am also eager to grow as a full<br>stak <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">develop</span>per.<br>+62 851-7520-0686<br>mohsyaefuleffendi@gmail.com I enjoy learning new things, especially those related to web<br>technologies, programming, and system <span style=\"background-color: yellow\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow\">develop</span>ment</span>. Currently,<br>http://bit.ly/3xyHqbY I am focusing on API <span style=\"background-color: yellow\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow\">develop</span>ment</span>, database <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">management</span>, and<br>modern frameworks such as React JS and Flask.<br>Jawa Barat, Kabupaten<br>Cirebon, Desa Palimanan<br>In addition, I am continuously improving my front-end skills to<br>Barat<br>build applications that are not only functional but also offer a<br>great user <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">experience</span>. I am open to internship opportunities,<br>KEMAMPUAN <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">project</span> collaborations, or discussions related to <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">technology</span> and<br>programming.<br>EDUCATION<br>Mudah berkomunikasi<br>Mudah bergaul SMA Negeri 1 Palimanan<br>2021-2024 | Jurusan MIPA<br>Aktif dalam berorganisasi<br>Peraih Medali Emas Matematika Olimpiade AKSI<br>Peraih Medali Emas Fisika Olimpiade AKSI<br>Peraih Medali Emas Kimia Olimpiade AKSI<br>Peraih Medali Emas Biologi Olimpiade AKSI<br>Juara 1 Basket Putra 2022 Tingkat Kabulaten<br>Juara 3 Basket Putra 2023 Tingkat Kabupaten<br>Universitas Sebelas Maret<br>2024-SEKARANG |<br>Peserta Web Design International<br>Competion GAYATAMA UNESA<br>HOBI SAYA<br>Ketua Devisi Media Komunikasi HIMA<br>Peserta OLIVIA 2025<br>Bermain Basket Peserta GEMASTIK 2025<br>Bermain Gitar<br>PENGALAMAN<br>Berlari<br>Fotografer Mengikuti Ekstrakurikuler Olahraga, menjadi Devisi<br>Dokumentasi dan berpartisipasi menjadi<br>Belajar Bahasa<br>penanggung jawab dalam beberapa acara di<br>Pemrograman sekolah<br>Mengikuti beberapa olimpiade akademik maupun<br>Ngoding<br>nonakademik<br>Mengikuti beberapa seminar', 'Example of IT Job Description\nPowered by www.VelvetJobs.com\nOur company is growing rapidly and is looking for an IT. To join our growing team,\nplease review the list of responsibilities and qualifications.\nResponsibilities for IT\nWorking with Problem Owners, prepare Root Cause Analysis reports and/or\nExecutive Summary reports\nDaily follow-up on action items related to open Problem Records\nWeekly and monthly Problem Management reporting\nCompile and analyze metrics for Incidents and Problems\nProvide off hours systems support as part of on-call rotation, if required\nThe chosen candidate must have strong technical, analytical and problem\nsolving skills with proven experience delivering complex technology projects\nExperience in Master Data (InfoSphere Master Data Management preferred) ,\nand ETL (InfoSphere Information Server (DataStage/QualityStage) preferred)\nprocessing an asset\nDevelop effective solutions by researching/analyzing issues, defining\nopportunities for technical process improvements and making\nrecommendations\nProvide guidance and/or consulting service to the technology team and\ntechnology partners\nSubject Matter Expert who consults with clients and/or project teams,\nassuming the lead role\nQualifications for IT\nAssist with environment management and maintenance\nPrimary responsibility for incident resolution\nCollege / University with emphasis on computer science and business or\nIT Industry accreditions not required, but will be considered along with\nexperience\nSound knowledge and experience in Systems/Application Development,\nProject Management, and Financial Management\nKnowledge of Derivative workflow from pricing to payments', '[{\"judul\": \"Kata Kunci Teknis Tidak Ditemukan\", \"saran\": \"Beberapa istilah penting dari deskripsi pekerjaan tidak ditemukan di CV Anda. Ini bisa membuat sistem atau HR menganggap Anda kurang relevan dengan posisi ini.\\n\"}, {\"judul\": \"Detail Pengalaman Tidak Jelas\", \"saran\": \"Tampilkan pengalaman kerja Anda dengan durasi (misalnya \'2 tahun sebagai Web Developer\'). Durasi penting untuk menilai tingkat pengalaman Anda.\"}, {\"judul\": \"Soft Skills Kurang Terlihat\", \"saran\": \"Soft skills juga penting. Pertimbangkan untuk menambahkan poin tentang kemampuan seperti: komunikasi, kerja tim, adaptasi, atau kepemimpinan.\"}, {\"judul\": \"Gunakan Bahasa Profesional\", \"saran\": \"Beberapa kata yang digunakan terdengar terlalu informal untuk CV, seperti: aku. Gunakan bahasa yang profesional dan netral.\"}]', 26.05, '2026-05-08 02:01:51'),
(71, 38, 'MOH. SYAEFUL EFFENDI<br>Student of Informatic Engineering Sebelas Maret University<br>Cirebon, Jawa Barat, Indonesia<br>ABOUT ME<br>I am a student in the Diploma Program (D3) of Informatics<br>KONTAK<br>Engineering at Sebelas Maret University. I have a strong interest<br>in back-end <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">develop</span>ment, but I am also eager to grow as a full<br>stak <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">develop</span>per.<br>+62 851-7520-0686<br>mohsyaefuleffendi@gmail.com I enjoy learning new things, especially those related to web<br>technologies, programming, and system <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">develop</span>ment. Currently,<br>http://bit.ly/3xyHqbY I am focusing on API <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">develop</span>ment, database <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">management</span>, and<br>modern frameworks such as React JS and Flask.<br>Jawa Barat, Kabupaten<br>Cirebon, Desa Palimanan<br>In addition, I am continuously improving my front-end skills to<br>Barat<br>build applications that are not only functional but also offer a<br>great user <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">experience</span>. I am open to internship opportunities,<br>KEMAMPUAN <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">project</span> collaborations, or discussions related to <span style=\"background-color: yellow\">technology</span> and<br>programming.<br>EDUCATION<br>Mudah berkomunikasi<br>Mudah bergaul SMA Negeri 1 Palimanan<br>2021-2024 | Jurusan MIPA<br>Aktif dalam berorganisasi<br>Peraih Medali Emas Matematika Olimpiade AKSI<br>Peraih Medali Emas Fisika Olimpiade AKSI<br>Peraih Medali Emas Kimia Olimpiade AKSI<br>Peraih Medali Emas Biologi Olimpiade AKSI<br>Juara 1 Basket Putra 2022 Tingkat Kabulaten<br>Juara 3 Basket Putra 2023 Tingkat Kabupaten<br>Universitas Sebelas Maret<br>2024-SEKARANG |<br>Peserta Web Design International<br>Competion GAYATAMA UNESA<br>HOBI SAYA<br>Ketua Devisi Media Komunikasi HIMA<br>Peserta OLIVIA 2025<br>Bermain Basket Peserta GEMASTIK 2025<br>Bermain Gitar<br>PENGALAMAN<br>Berlari<br>Fotografer Mengikuti Ekstrakurikuler Olahraga, menjadi Devisi<br>Dokumentasi dan berpartisipasi menjadi<br>Belajar Bahasa<br>penanggung jawab dalam beberapa acara di<br>Pemrograman sekolah<br>Mengikuti beberapa olimpiade akademik maupun<br>Ngoding<br>nonakademik<br>Mengikuti beberapa seminar', 'Example of IT Job Description\nPowered by www.VelvetJobs.com\nOur company is growing rapidly and is looking for an IT. To join our growing team,\nplease review the list of responsibilities and qualifications.\nResponsibilities for IT\nWorking with Problem Owners, prepare Root Cause Analysis reports and/or\nExecutive Summary reports\nDaily follow-up on action items related to open Problem Records\nWeekly and monthly Problem Management reporting\nCompile and analyze metrics for Incidents and Problems\nProvide off hours systems support as part of on-call rotation, if required\nThe chosen candidate must have strong technical, analytical and problem\nsolving skills with proven experience delivering complex technology projects\nExperience in Master Data (InfoSphere Master Data Management preferred) ,\nand ETL (InfoSphere Information Server (DataStage/QualityStage) preferred)\nprocessing an asset\nDevelop effective solutions by researching/analyzing issues, defining\nopportunities for technical process improvements and making\nrecommendations\nProvide guidance and/or consulting service to the technology team and\ntechnology partners\nSubject Matter Expert who consults with clients and/or project teams,\nassuming the lead role\nQualifications for IT\nAssist with environment management and maintenance\nPrimary responsibility for incident resolution\nCollege / University with emphasis on computer science and business or\nIT Industry accreditions not required, but will be considered along with\nexperience\nSound knowledge and experience in Systems/Application Development,\nProject Management, and Financial Management\nKnowledge of Derivative workflow from pricing to payments', '[{\"judul\": \"Kata Kunci Teknis Tidak Ditemukan\", \"saran\": \"Beberapa istilah penting dari deskripsi pekerjaan tidak ditemukan di CV Anda. Ini bisa membuat sistem atau HR menganggap Anda kurang relevan dengan posisi ini.\\n\"}, {\"judul\": \"Detail Pengalaman Tidak Jelas\", \"saran\": \"Tampilkan pengalaman kerja Anda dengan durasi (misalnya \'2 tahun sebagai Web Developer\'). Durasi penting untuk menilai tingkat pengalaman Anda.\"}, {\"judul\": \"Soft Skills Kurang Terlihat\", \"saran\": \"Soft skills juga penting. Pertimbangkan untuk menambahkan poin tentang kemampuan seperti: komunikasi, kerja tim, adaptasi, atau kepemimpinan.\"}, {\"judul\": \"Gunakan Bahasa Profesional\", \"saran\": \"Beberapa kata yang digunakan terdengar terlalu informal untuk CV, seperti: aku. Gunakan bahasa yang profesional dan netral.\"}]', 26.05, '2026-05-12 04:34:12');

