(157, 'Tentang pekerjaan ini\nLowongan ini berasal dari bursa lowongan pekerjaan. Pelajari Lebih Lanjut\nQualification\nMinimal pendidikan S1 Teknik Sipil\nMinimal pengalaman 3-5 tahun di bidang yang sama\nFamiliar dan mampu menggunakan software software civil\nMampu mebuat BoQ, RAB, RAP, danmelakukan control pekerjaan\nMemiliki keterampilan komunikasi dan manajemen proyek.\nJob Description\nMerencanakan proyek pekerjaan, melakukan survei tanah dan mengumpulkan data\nMembuat gambar dengan software drawing dan perhitungan struktural untuk memastikan kekuatan dan\nkeamanan pekerjaan\nMembantu tim sipil dalam pelaksanaan proyek\nMembuat RAB bangunan dan mengerti konstruksi gedung\nBisa menganalisa permasalahan bangunan gedung dan follow up pekerjaanya\nBersedia ditugaskan di Site seluruh Indonesia.', 'uploads\\CV_Dewantoro_Kuncoro_Wahyu_Utomo_-_Dewantoro_Kuncoro.pdf', 81.1906, 26, 'Dewantoro Kuncoro Wahyu Utomo\nGlagahwangi, Polanharjo, Klaten, Jawa Tengah - Indonesia dewantoro812@gmail.com 081352741851\nEXPERIENCE\nPT Kalimantan Prima Persada Kaliorang, Kalimantan Timur, Indonesia\nGeneral Service & Group Leader Civil Construction Feb 2022 - Present\nŸ Bertanggung Jawab dalam Pengawasan / Supervisi Project Meliputi Pengawasan Quality Control\nPekerjaan, Time Frame Scedule Pekerjaan, Persiapan Lahan serta K3LH di Setiap Area Project.\nŸ Bertanggung Jawab dalam Maintenance Bangunan Meliputi Daily Report and Maintenance Building,\nInspeksi Bangunan untuk Seluruh Asset Bangunan di Area Pertambangan.\nŸ Bertanggung Jawab dalam Pengadaan Barang dan Jasa Meliputi Cost Control Management, General\nRequest, Stock Management Serta Monitoring Harga Barang dan Jasa Sesuai dengan IBS.\nŸ Pembuatan Shopdrawing Project dari Perencanaan Siteplan Hingga Detail Design Engineering Meliputi\nGambar 3D dan 2D Bangunan.\nŸ Pembuatan BOQ dan Estimasi Biaya Project Meliputi Perhitungan Volume Pekerjaan Hingga Perencanaan\nAnggaran Biaya.\nŸ Pengadaan Tender dan Administrasi Sipil Meliputi Pemilihan Vendor, Aanwijzing, Pembuatan SPK /\nKontrak Kerja, Hingga Pembayaran Invoice Konstruksi Sipil.\nŸ General Service Meliputi Service Mess dan Catering Mess.\nTarakota Architecture Bekasi, Jawa Barat, Indonesia\nDrafter Engineering Sept 2021 - Des 2021\nŸ Pembuatan Shopdrawing Project Meliputi Detail Design Engineering.\nŸ Pembuatan BOQ dan Estimasi Biaya Project Meliputi Perhitungan Volume Pekerjaan Hingga Perencanaan\nAnggaran Biaya.\nŸ Analisa Structure Meliputi Perencanaan Pembebanan Bangunan Serta Analisa Gempa.\nEDUCATION\nUniversitas Sebelas Maret Surakarta 2017 - 2020\nD3 Teknik Sipil Infrastruktur Perkotaan\nŸ Juara 1 Fiber Reinforced Concrete Bowling Ball Competition 2018 Trisakti.\nŸ Asisten Dosen Mata Kuliah Praktikum Bahan Bangunan.\nŸ Kepala Bidang 3 Himpunan Mahasiswa Diploma Teknik Sipil UNS.\nŸ Staff Bagian Kemahasiswaan Himpunan Mahasiswa Diploma Teknik Sipil UNS.\nSMK N 2 Surakarta 2014 - 2017\nTeknik Komputer dan Jaringan\nADDITIONAL INFORMATION\nŸ Techniques : Leadership, Desain Thinking, Team Work, Problem Solving, Time Management.\nŸ Technical Skills : AutoCAD, SketchUp, SAP2000, MS Office, CorelDraw X7.\nŸ Certifications : Sertifikat Keterampilan Kerja Quantity Surveyor LPJK Provinsi Jawa Tengah, Sertifikat\nKeterampilan Kerja Pelaksana Lapangan Pekerjaan Perumahan dan Gedung LPJK Provinsi Jawa Tengah.', 'uploads\\CV_Irvan_Yoga_Pratama_-_Irvan_Yoga_Pratama.pdf', 'uploads\\CV_Rosyihan_Caesar_N_-_Rosyihan_Caesar_Nurrohman.pdf', 45.4333, 17.5451, 'Irvan Yoga Pratama\nSukoharjo, Indonesia\n+6285642106990 (WA)\nE-mail: irvanyoga20@gmail.com\nLinkedIn: www.linkedin.com/in/irvan-yoga-pratama/\nSummary\nA fresh graduate from Sebelas Maret University (UNS) who has complete a Diploma 3\nmajoring in mechanical engineering. He is able to demonstrate good analytical, teamwork,\ntime management and communication skill while successfully maintain above 3.5 GPA. Seeks\nopportunities to benefit knowledge learned and experience earned alongside professionals.\nEventual career goal is to secure a position at a company where I can continue to grow and\nimprove myself both personally and professionally.\nEducation\n2020-2023 Diploma 3 of Mechanical Engineering\nUniversitas Sebelas Maret Surakarta\nGPA 3,71/4,00\nFinal Project : Power and Transmission Narrow Tilting Tricycle on Electric\nBike\n2016-2019 Light Vehicle Engineering\nState Vocational School 2 Surakarta\nWorking Experience\n2022 Internship at PT Hasil Karya Indonesia (HKI)\n- The internship runs for 2 months (November-December 2022)\n- Learn about HKI CNC Machine\n- Learn about how to operate HKI CNC Machine with manual programing\n- Learn to design some parts with G-Code and M-Code then processed in\nHKI CNC Machine\n2022 Lecturer Assistant\n- Worked with team, 3 people in total including myself for six months\n(September-December 2022)\n- Lead and monitoring of Practical Electric Circuits Course\n- Make a exam every week and make a record at end of semester\n- Guide to make report of Practical Electric Circuits\n2022 Internship at CV. Sampoerna Prima Gemilang\n- The internship runs for 2 months on 18 July - 17 August 2022\n- Drawing a part of Ice Tube Machine with SolidWork and Mach3, then\nProcesses to CNC Plasma Cutting\n- Design the piping part of Hydraulic Rolling Machine\n- Re-Drawing CNC Plasma Cutting Machine with SolidWork\n2019-2020 Production Operator PT. Astra Honda Motor\n- Worked with team, 13 people in total including myself\n- Assembling some part of steering handle in GenSub Assy Wheel\nDepartment\n- Keep the work area clean and safe\nOrganization Experience\n2021 Himpunan Mahasiswa Diploma III Mesin (HMDM SV UNS)\n- Worked as member of development of interest and talents division\n- Running a Solidarity Cup’s and handle E-Sports race\n- Hold the selection of prospective players of E-sports race for Insting Cup’s\nHardskill\nDocument\nMicrosoft Word, Microsoft Power Point, Microsoft Excel\nDesign Manufacture\nSolidworks, MasterCAM\nManufacture\nCNC Machine, Welding, Machining\nSoftskill\nEnglish, Detail oriented, Problem solving, Communication skill, Time management\nCertificate\n- TOEIC Certificate Score 495\n- Welding Engineer BNSP\n- Certificate Of Competence CNC Basic Operation for HKI – Tech Control', 'DATA PRIBADI\nTempat, Tanggal Lahir\nSurakarta, 18 April 2002\nJenis Kelamin\nLaki-laki\nAgama\nIslam\nStatus\nBelum Menikah\nRosyihan Caesar\nPENDIDIKAN\nNurrohman\nUniversitas Sebelas Maret (2020-2023)\nsaya merupakan lulusan dari (DIII Teknik Sipil - IPK 3,62)\nprogram studi DIII Teknik Sipil SMAN 4 Surakarta (2017-2020)\nUniversitas Sebelas Maret yang SMPN 1 Surakarta (2013-2017)\nmemiliki tanggung jawab tinggi,\ndisiplin, memiliki kemauan belajar PENGALAMAN\ntinggi, dan tekun untuk setiap tugas\nOrganisasi\nserta mampu menggunakan\nberbagai aplikasi ke teknik sipilan. Staff Medinfo HMDS Fondasi (Februari\n2021 - November 2021)\nKoordinator Publikasi dan Dokumentasi\nKEAHLIAN\nAgregat 6.0 (Juni 2021 - Oktober 2021)\nAUTOCAD\nKerja Praktik\nREVIT\nProyek Gedung Parkir RS. Roemani\nSKETCHUP\nSemarang (4 Juli 2022- 4 September 2022)\nLUMION\nHOBI\nMS. OFFICE\nADOBE PREMIERE\nOtomotif\nADOBE AFTER EFFECT\nGame\nKONTAK\nVIdeo editing\nBAHASA\n085156396391\nJl. Anggur II No. 24 Wonorejo,\nBahasa Indonesia\nGondangrejo, Karanganyar\nBahasa Inggris\nrosyirohman@gmail.com', '2025-08-03 04:17:46'),
(158, 'Tentang pekerjaan ini\nLowongan ini berasal dari bursa lowongan pekerjaan. Pelajari Lebih Lanjut\nQualification\nMinimal pendidikan S1 Teknik Sipil\nMinimal pengalaman 3-5 tahun di bidang yang sama\nFamiliar dan mampu menggunakan software software civil\nMampu mebuat BoQ, RAB, RAP, danmelakukan control pekerjaan\nMemiliki keterampilan komunikasi dan manajemen proyek.\nJob Description\nMerencanakan proyek pekerjaan, melakukan survei tanah dan mengumpulkan data\nMembuat gambar dengan software drawing dan perhitungan struktural untuk memastikan kekuatan dan\nkeamanan pekerjaan\nMembantu tim sipil dalam pelaksanaan proyek\nMembuat RAB bangunan dan mengerti konstruksi gedung\nBisa menganalisa permasalahan bangunan gedung dan follow up pekerjaanya\nBersedia ditugaskan di Site seluruh Indonesia.', 'uploads\\Curriculum_Vitae_Hariarti_Hersiati_-_Hariarti_Hersiati.pdf', 84.9886, 26, 'Hariarti Hersiati\nPejagoan, Kebumen, Jawa Tengah, 54361\n+62859-1446-98761\nhariartihersiati2309@gmail.com\nlinkedin.com/in/hariarti-hersiati-954051249/\nPENDIDIKAN DAN PELATIHAN\nUniversitas Sebelas Maret Himpunan Mahasiswa Sipil FT UNS\nD3 Teknik Sipil Transportasi “Pelatihan SketchUp”\n(Agustus 2019 – Juni 2022) November 2020\nLulus dengan IPK 3,76 / 4,00\nAnak Teknik Indonesia\nDentech Corporation\n“Basic Training Autocad” “SAP2000 For Modeling & Analysis Structure –\nNovember 2022 Introduction”\nSeptember 2020\nHimpunan Mahasiswa Diploma Sipil SV UNS\n“BIM Hands- On Training”\nFebruari 2021\nPENGALAMAN KERJA\nPT. SUNDUS KARYA PERDANA  Bertanggung j awab dalam mengadministrasi rangkaian proses\nAdministrasi Manajemen Proyek tender/lelang. Dimulai dari membuat dokumen penawaran,\ndokumen kualifikasi, dokumen kontrak sampai dengan\nJuli 2022 - Sekarang\ndokumen pencairan,\n Membuat surat jalan/nota pengiriman untuk material dan alat\nberat untuk kegiatan konstruksi,\n Mengurus pajak dan BPJS ketenagakerjaan perusahaan.\n Bertanggungjawab dalam membantu pelaksana lapangan untuk\nPT. Asri Jaya Putra Perkasa memonitoring jalannya pekerjaan di proyek dan membuat\nlaporan kemajuan proyek seperti laporan harian, laporan\nAssistant Quality Control\nmingguan dan laporan bulanan.\nAgustus – Oktober 2021\nPRESTASI KOMPETENSI, SOFTWARE DAN BAHASA\nJuara 2  Sertifikasi Kompetensi “Kesehatan dan Keselamatan Kerja\nLomba Aspal Nasional Civil Classical (K3)”,\nFest  AutoCAD,\nUniversitas Muhammadiyah Yogyakarta  SketchUp,\n2021  SAP 2000,\nRunner Up 2  Ms.Excel, Ms. Word, Ms. Power Point, Ms. Office, Ms. Teams,\nAdobe Photoshop,\nLomba Aspal Nasional Civil Classical\n Bahasa Indonesia, Bahasa Inggris.\nFest\nUniversitas Muhammadiyah Yogyakarta\n2020\nPENGALAMAN ORGANISASI\nDepartemen Kesejahteraan Mahasiswa  Sebagai penghubung antara mahasiswa dengan pihak\nHMDS,Staff, Februari 2020 prodi melalui forum aspirasi.', 'uploads\\Curriculum_Vitae_-_Faizal_Rahmadi_Akbar.pdf', 'uploads\\Curriculum_Vitae_CV_-_Yuliana_Prasetiyani_-_Yuliana_Prasetiyani.pdf', 81.7172, 44.1705, 'Faizal Rahmadi Akbar, A.Md.T\nPhone : 089624053472 | Email : faizal90akbar@gmail.com | Addres : Kebumen, Jawa Tengah,\nIndonesia, 54316\nMechanical Engineering\nProfil Personal\nSaya merupakan lulusan Diploma 3 Teknik Mesin dari Universitas Sebelas Maret\nSurakarta. Saya merupakan pribadi yang aktif dalam organisasi baik di internal\nmaupun eksternal kampus. Saya memiliki pengalaman magang di salah satu BUMN\nyaitu PT. Krakatau Perbengkelan dan Perawatan. Saya juga pernah menjadi asisten\ndosen semasa menjalani perkuliahan. Saya siap untuk bekerja secara individu\nmaupun dalam kelompok. Saya memiliki dedikasi yang tinggi terhadap tanggung\njawab yang saya terima.\nRiwayat Pendidikan\nUniversitas Sebelas Maret – Surakarta, Jawa Tengah (2019-2022)\nD3 Teknik Mesin – IPK 3.59\n• Desain, manufactur, machining, motor bakar, dan material.\nSertifikat\n• Mechanical Design (Solid Works) from Dassault Systemes, Surakarta 2022.\nPengalaman Magang\nPT. Krakatau Perbengkelan dan Perawatan (Juni - Agustus 2021)\nQuality Control\n• Mengecek kesesuaian dimensi.\n• Mengecek kesesuaian bentuk dan kelurusan.\n• Mengecek kualitas pengelasan (visual).\n• Mengecek kesesuaian ketebalan coating.\nPengalaman Organisasi\n• Staff Internal Himpunan Mahasiswa Diploma Teknik Mesin UNS.\n• Staff minat dan bakat Himpunan Mahasiswa Kebumen – Solo.\n• Anggota Forum Mahasiswa Mesin Surakarta.\nKemampuan Teknikal\n• Pengoperasian mesin bubut, milling, dan hand tools.\n• Pengoperasian software design (AutoCad, Autodesk Fusion 360, Solid Works).\n• Pengoperasian welding.', 'Yuliana Prasetiyani\n085-870-642-461 | yulianaprasetiyani790@gmail.com | www.linkedin.com/in/yuliana-prasetiyani\nParit, RT:15/RW:00, Karangpelem, Kedawung, Sragen, Central Java\nFresh graduate of the Diploma III Chemical Engineering study program at Sebelas Maret University. Has\nexperience in the fields of energy and mineral resources. I am a brave and open-minded person. I have\nexperience in various organizations and internships, so I have good management, leadership skills and\ncan easily adapt to a dynamic work environment.\nEDUCATION\nSebelas Maret University – Surakarta, Central Java Jul 2020 – Jul 2023\nDiploma III Chemical Engineering Major, GPA 3.87 / 4.00\nFinal Project: Synthesis of Na-NMC Material with Combination Method as Cathode for Sodium Ion Battery.\nRelevant education: Health Safety Work and Labour Law Course.\nACHIEVEMENT\nGraduated on time with Cumlaude Predicate Jul 2023\nPublication of the national journal Jul 2023\n• \"The Conversion of Sorghum (Sorghum bicolor (L.) Moench) Stem Waste into Activated Carbon by the Pyrolysis\nMethod Using ZnCl \", Equilibrium Journal of Chemical Engineering, Vol.7 No.2, 107-115, 2023.\n2\nWORK EXPERIENCE\nPPSDM Migas – Blora, Central Java Jan 2023\nStudent Intern, Refinery Department\n• Evaluating the performance of the C-4 stripper based on mass balance and heat balance calculations to obtain an\nefficiency of 87.12%.\n• Verify the instrumentation on the refinery units and obtain data from DCS and the refinery\'s instrumentation tools.\n• Experienced in the oil and gas industry about operational processes, equipment, utilities, and fire extinguishers in\nthe refinery unit.\n• Examine the production testing laboratory\'s testing procedure, which includes determining the raw materials\' and\nproducts\' quality.\nPUI-PT Teknologi Penyimpanan energi Listrik UNS – Surakarta, Central Java Jul 2022 – Aug 2022\nStudent Intern, Battery Producing Industry\n• Carrying out synthesis for the manufacture of NMC 622 precursors.\n• Assembling NMC lithium cylindrical batteries.\n• Testing and charging the lithium battery NMC.\nSebelas Maret University – Surakarta, Central Java\n• Assistant of Bioprocess Practicum Feb 2023 – Jul 2023\n• Assistant of Process I Practicum Aug 2022 – Jan 2023\n• Assistant of Physical and Chemistry Practicum Feb 2022 – Jun 2022\n• Assistant of Aplied Physics Practicum Sep 2021 – Jan 2022\nORGANIZATIONAL EXPERIENCE\nKADIKA SV UNS – Surakarta, Central Java Jan 2022 – Dec 2022\nSecretary and treasurer of the education and professional department\n• Handling the secretariat, such as managing correspondence, proposals, preparing PowerPoint, notules, revising\nLPJs, as well as other documents required by the education and professional departments.\n• Prepare RAB, SPJ, and files related to the finances department.\n• Manage member cash and finances during one period.\nKADIKA SV UNS – Surakarta, Central Java Jan 2021 – Dec 2021\nStaff of Jaringan Department\n• Establish good relationships with internal and external parties KADIKA SV UNS.\n• Assist in carrying out the department\'s job plan during one period.\n• Responsible for implementing the work program, called Bina Desa KADIKA 2021.\nTRAINING AND CERTIFICATION\nEnerCoSS X BKKMTKI D IV Oct 2023\n• Training ISO 50001: Energy Management System\n• Training ISO 14001: Environmental Management System\n• Training ISO 45001: Occupational Health and Safety\nACTIVITIES AND PROJECT\nStaff Liaison Officer Basic Organizational Exercises BKKMTKI D III 2021\nIn charge of serving as the point of contact for visitors and the organizing team.\nPOLIMER KADIKA 2021\nMembers of the creative team and disciplinary committee in leadership training activities are expected to develop new\nstudents\' soft skills, such as great leadership, design thinking, and good public speaking.\nPKKMB Sebelas Maret University 2020\nSupervises activities to introduce the campus environment to new students and is responsible for being the operator for\nthe 2020 PKKMB UNS student record virtual paper mob.\nSKILL AND INTEREST\nHard-skill Chemical industrial processes, chemical analysis, Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Power Point), Google\nSuites, Canva, CorelDraw, Matlab, AutoCAD Plant 3D, Imagej, and Origin.\nSoft-skill Good communication skills, collaboration, problem solving, thoroughness and accuracy.\nLanguage Indonesia (Native), English (Elementary Proficiency).\nInterest Constraction Company, Safety Health and Environtment (SHE) division, Quality Assurance and Quality\nControll.', '2025-08-03 04:19:21'),
